
Project Overview: Day Trip Advisor
add openweather support with public api
Goal: Generate day trip plans based on a city and simulated weather, persisting the result to different S3 buckets based on the weather condition.
Components:
Lambda: Simulates weather (Sunny/Snowy) with OpenTelemetry instrumentation.
Bedrock Guardrail: Blocks Health/Financial advice.
Bedrock Prompt: Generates the itinerary using the Nova Micro model.
Bedrock Flow: Orchestrates the input, Lambda, Prompt, logic, and S3 persistence.

